<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:Roma_flag.svg" class="image" title="Flag of the Roma people"><img alt="Flag of the Roma people" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2f/Roma_flag.svg/40px-Roma_flag.svg.png" width="40" height="27" border="0" /></a></div>
<p><b>Cultural groups</b><br />
<b>Roma</b> (<a href="/wiki/Boyash" title="Boyash">Boyash</a> • <a href="/wiki/Kalderash" title="Kalderash">Kalderash</a> • <a href="/wiki/Lovari_(Roma)" title="Lovari (Roma)">Lovari</a> • <a href="/wiki/Machvaya" title="Machvaya">Machvaya</a> •<a href="/wiki/Ruska_Roma" title="Ruska Roma">Ruska Roma</a>• <a href="/wiki/Servitko_Roma" title="Servitko Roma">Servitko Roma</a>• <a href="/wiki/Ursari" title="Ursari">Ursari</a> •<a href="/wiki/Muslim_Roma" title="Muslim Roma">Muslim Roma</a>) •<a href="/wiki/Ashkali" title="Ashkali">Ashkali</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Spain" title="Roma in Spain" class="mw-redirect">Gitanos</a> • <a href="/wiki/Finnish_Kale" title="Finnish Kale">Finnish Kale</a> • <a href="/wiki/Kale_(Welsh_Romanies)" title="Kale (Welsh Romanies)">Welsh Kale</a> • <a href="/wiki/Romnichal" title="Romnichal" class="mw-redirect">Romnichal</a> •<a href="/wiki/Sinti" title="Sinti">Sinti</a> •<a href="/wiki/Manouche" title="Manouche" class="mw-redirect">Manouche</a> • <a href="/wiki/Norwegian_and_Swedish_Travellers" title="Norwegian and Swedish Travellers">Scandinavian Travellers (Tavinger, Romanisæl)</a> • <a href="/wiki/Kawliya" title="Kawliya">Kawliya</a><br />
(sometimes considered Romani: <a href="/wiki/Dom_people" title="Dom people">Dom</a> • <a href="/wiki/Lom_people" title="Lom people">Lom</a> • <a href="/wiki/Lyuli" title="Lyuli">Lyuli</a> • <a href="/wiki/Bosha_(Roma)" title="Bosha (Roma)" class="mw-redirect">Bosha</a> • <a href="/wiki/Garachi" title="Garachi">Garachi</a>)<br /></p>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Romani_people_by_country" title="Romani people by country">By location</a>:</b><br />
Central and Eastern Europe: <a href="/wiki/Roma_minority_in_Croatia" title="Roma minority in Croatia">Croatia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_minority_in_Bosnia_and_Herzegovina" title="Roma minority in Bosnia and Herzegovina">Bosnia and Herzegovina</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Bulgaria" title="Roma in Bulgaria">Bulgaria</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_of_Greece" title="Roma people of Greece" class="mw-redirect">Greece</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_of_Hungary" title="Roma people of Hungary" class="mw-redirect">Hungary</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Kosovo" title="Roma in Kosovo">Kosovo</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_the_Republic_of_Macedonia" title="Roma in the Republic of Macedonia">Macedonia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_minority_in_Romania" title="Roma minority in Romania">Romania</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_in_Russia" title="Roma people in Russia" class="mw-redirect">Russia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_of_Serbia" title="Roma people of Serbia" class="mw-redirect">Serbia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_of_Slovakia" title="Roma people of Slovakia" class="mw-redirect">Slovakia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Romani_people_in_Spain" title="Romani people in Spain">Spain</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Turkey" title="Roma in Turkey">Turkey</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_minority_in_Ukraine" title="Roma minority in Ukraine" class="mw-redirect">Ukraine</a><br />
Western and Northern Europe: <a href="/wiki/Finnish_Roma" title="Finnish Roma" class="mw-redirect">Finland</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_people_of_France" title="Roma people of France" class="mw-redirect">France</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Spain" title="Roma in Spain" class="mw-redirect">Spain</a> •<br />
Near East: <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Armenia" title="Roma in Armenia" class="mw-redirect">Armenia</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_minority_in_Syria" title="Roma minority in Syria" class="mw-redirect">Syria</a> •<br />
Americas: <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Brazil" title="Roma in Brazil" class="mw-redirect">Brazil</a> • <a href="/wiki/Black_Dutch" title="Black Dutch">Black Dutch (USA)</a><br /></p>
<p><b>Settlements and communities</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/Sulukule" title="Sulukule">Sulukule</a> • <a href="/wiki/Agia_Varvara" title="Agia Varvara">Agia Varvara</a> • <a href="/wiki/Roma_in_Mitrovica_Camps" title="Roma in Mitrovica Camps">Mitrovica refugee camps</a> • <a href="/wiki/Stolipinovo" title="Stolipinovo">Stolipinovo</a> • <a href="/wiki/Rudolice_nad_B%C3%ADlinou" title="Rudolice nad Bílinou">Rudolice nad Bílinou</a> • <a href="/wiki/%C5%A0uto_Orizari_municipality" title="Šuto Orizari municipality" class="mw-redirect">Šuto Orizari municipality</a> • <a href="/wiki/Banglade%C5%A1" title="Bangladeš">Bangladeš</a> • <a href="/wiki/Bude%C5%9Fti" title="Budeşti">Budeşti</a> • <a href="/wiki/Jatagan_Mala" title="Jatagan Mala">Jatagan Mala</a> • <a href="/wiki/Zanea" title="Zanea">Zanea</a></p>
